{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtextcomponenttokensprovider\/inputtextcolorbgdefaulthover"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider\/inputTextColorBgDefaultHover","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"inputTextColorBgDefaultHover","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"inputTextColorBgDefaultHover","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens"}],"role":"symbol","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B37ThemeInputTextComponentTokensProviderC05inputE19ColorBgDefaultHover18OUDSTokensSemantic08MultiplejoG0Cvp","symbolKind":"property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Inherited from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"InputTextComponentTokens.inputTextColorBgDefaultHover"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"inputTextColorBgDefaultHover"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of input text","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"input text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSInputText","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllInputTextComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"InouttextComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"input text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Inout text","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), colors ("},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtextcomponenttokensprovider","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","role":"collection","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider/inputTextColorBgDefaultHover":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"inputTextColorBgDefaultHover","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens","text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethem